title: ZX Spectrum TOSEC-based set v2017-11-06 by Lady Eklipse
description: This is the ultimate, most complete ZX Spectrum files set that have ever been! This set contains: - All files that were in TOSEC; - All files from www.worldofspectrum.org which were never in TOSEC before; - All modern homebrews up to September 2017; - Demos from pouet.net; - Games which took part in Crap Games Competition; - Rare hacks and compilations. Provided by Lady Eklipse with love to all ZX Spectrum community. 31. October, 2017 If you want an easy way to sort these files any way you want, please check out ZX Pokemaster: https://sourceforge.net/projects/zx-pokemaster/ If you have any propositions or complaints please contact me: via or email: eklipse2009 [at]
